(179, 1, '2021-10-31 00:05:46', '2021-10-31 00:07:47', '2021-10-30', '23:40:00', NULL, 'EDT', 14400, 'How my ×©×‘×ª was', 'I walked to the Young Israel of Woodmere for Friday night ×ª×¤×™×œ×” and spoke to Rabbi Axelrod after ×ª×¤×™×œ×” about anyone that has Aspergerâ€™s and he told me that he got my email and that heâ€™s going to help me but it will take some time. He realized that I push friends too hard by the fact that I walked from Far Rockaway to Woodmere just to find friends. The Rabbi also told me to do ×ª×¤×™×œ×” locally but I said Far Rockaway is too yeshivish so he suggested to me the Young Israel of Lawrence-Cedarhurst which I did ×ª×¤×™×œ×” there for a while. I did ×©×—×¨×™×ª at the Young Israel of Lawrence-Cedarhurst and had a ×§×™×“×•×© afterwards. I went to a friend from my elementary school in the afternoon and spoke for a little. I went to the Shteibel for ×ž× ×—×” due to my curiosity of what happened Thursday night with the person from IVDU that stared at me. I spoke to his father about this and he told me that his son is shy. I had a long conversation with his father about what Iâ€™m going through and how desperate for friends I am. He told me to stay for ×©×¢×•×“×” ×©×œ×™×©×™×ª and ×ž×¢×¨×™×‘ and that heâ€™ll drive me home afterwards which I did. I continued the conversation in the car ride home and curious where the other person that went to IVDU does ×ª×¤×™×œ×” and after a lot of guessing came to the conclusion that he does ×ª×¤×™×œ×” in the ×‘×™×ª ×ž×“×¨×© of Harborview. The question is how do I avoid being in defense mode with this person I knew from IVDU? How should I approach him? Should I even do ×©×—×¨×™×ª at the ×‘×™×ª ×ž×“×¨×© of Harborview to begin with? I am very anxious about this. He could be bothered by the fact that Iâ€™m stuck in the past or what I did in the Shteibel. I didnâ€™t really get along with him until the very end. I did end with him on a good note though but I still feel scared of how going to his shul would go about. 