(196, 1, '2021-11-08 22:05:09', '2021-11-08 22:05:09', '2021-11-08', '21:56:00', NULL, 'EST', 18000, 'My journey from work to college', 'I usually take the QM7 express bus from work to college which is a 2-stop one-seat ride. Unfortunately, my mask fell out of my pocket and the bus driver didnâ€™t have any. I quickly bought a mask from Bravo Pizza store and ran to catch the bus but after running for a half mile, gasping for breath, I gave up. I instead took the E train, sweaty and coughing the whole ride, to Kew Gardens-Union Turnpike station and transferred to the Q46 limited bus 2 stops to Union Turnpike/150 St which is where the QM7 leaves me off and walked to Landers College from there as usual. I didnâ€™t lose any time. The only setback was gasping for breath and crowding.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0),
(197, 1, '2021-11-08 22:22:26', '2021-11-08 22:22:26', '2021-11-08', '20:00:00', NULL, 'EST', 18000, 'My call from MASA Israel', 'I got an unexpected call from MASA Israel. I thought that it was a robocall at first so I acted silly like I always do when I get a robocall but that person was patient and told me that it was MASA Israel. I asked the lady on the phone if thereâ€™s anyone else in the program with Aspergerâ€™s and she said that there isnâ€™t. I told her that I have a lack of mindfulness and anxious if Iâ€™ll get along with someone that doesnâ€™t understand me and that Iâ€™ve never dormed or lived on my own before. She told me that she understands and that I could contact MASA Israel directly about programs for people with disabilities. She told me that sheâ€™s going to refund my application.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0),
(198, 1, '2021-11-09 03:54:40', '2021-11-09 03:54:40', '2021-11-09', '03:48:00', NULL, 'EST', 18000, 'How my college was', 'In database class, I learned more about subqueries and other functions. In Data Structures 1 class, I learned about sublists and costs and benefits. In Precalculus class, I learned about reflections and moved onto chapter 2. In fundamentals of Speech class, the professor brought in a camera and worked on timing speeches and the way you say it and also writing a speech to read it from a paper.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0),
