(200, 1, '2021-11-10 02:50:21', '2021-11-10 02:50:21', '2021-11-10', '02:43:00', NULL, 'EST', 18000, 'My first hangout with my training friend from Atlantic Beach', 'I went out to Sunflower Cafe for dinner with my training friend I met in Atlantic Beach. We talked about how to make friends and that it takes time to make friends. He also was trying to tell me that 2 people with Aspergerâ€™s canâ€™t really get along as roommates together because they donâ€™t understand how to socialize. He also mentioned to me a Jewish group in Manhattan for people with Aspergerâ€™s that play video games together but that itâ€™s only 18 and under but said that heâ€™ll try to get me in. After dinner, we went to the Young Israel of Woodmere for the 9PM ×ž×¢×¨×™×‘ and drove me home afterwards.', 'dinner-with-my-training-friend.jpg', 0, 'Dinner with my training friend', NULL, 0),
(201, 1, '2021-11-10 15:53:27', '2021-11-10 15:53:27', '2021-11-10', '15:51:00', NULL, 'EST', 18000, 'How work is going so far', 'Iâ€™m 2 hours into work but I canâ€™t get started on anything. Iâ€™m really depressed about college and how behind I am on the homeworks. Dropping classes would make it easier for me but my father would kick me out of the house if I drop even one class. He hates quitters.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0),
