(203, 1, '2021-11-11 02:54:56', '2021-11-11 02:54:56', '2021-11-11', '02:44:00', NULL, 'EST', 18000, 'How my college was', 'I took the train into college to come extra early so that I can speak to the office about dropping classes. I spoke to the school counselor and the disability department and the head of the technology department about this and made the decision to drop the non-computer classes. I then spoke to a student who knows me whoâ€™s almost done college and told me that I shouldnâ€™t drop Fundamentals of Speech because itâ€™s a very easy class and very easy to get an A so, at the end, I think Iâ€™ll just drop Precalculus. In database class, I learned about keywords Iâ€™ve never heard of before, like MERGE, SOURCE, and other keywords. In Data Structures 1 class, I learned about natural ordering. In Precalculus class, I learned about constraints. I then spoke to the professor at the end of class if itâ€™s a good idea to drop the class and he said yes. He told me that if I try my hardest from this point on, due to my low grades and missing homeworks, Iâ€™ll get a C. Thereâ€™s no Fundamentals of Speech class today.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0),
